    "A summary of the different models that we surveyed in Sect. 3.3 is presented in Table 15.",
    "It provides an overview for the purpose of selecting a particular model for developing a CAD system.",
    "Further, in the Tables 16 and 17 we compare the traditional ML and DL models respectively.",
    "With respect to the traditional ML models, most of the existing works use MRI scans from ADNI to train the classifiers.",
    "Though, these models concentrate on the feature engineering task for training the classifiers, their performance is comparatively lower to the DL models."
